ED_Title: Report of the International Court of Justice
ED_DecisionText: At its 23rd plenary meeting, on 28 October 2021, the General Assembly took note of the report of the International Court of Justice (footnote: A/76/4)
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/76/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
